	\draw[fill=black] (\t) circle (1pt) node[shift={(\g:8pt)}]{$ \t $};
}
\end{tikzpicture}

* a) Đúng. Vì $\overrightarrow{AM}-\overrightarrow{A N}=\overrightarrow{NM}$.
* b) Sai. Vì $\overrightarrow{MN}-\overrightarrow{NC}=\overrightarrow{MN}-\overrightarrow{MP}=\overrightarrow{PN}\ (\overrightarrow{NC}=\overrightarrow{MP})$.
* c) Đúng. Vì $\overrightarrow{MN}-\overrightarrow{PN}=\overrightarrow{MN}+\overrightarrow{NP}=\overrightarrow{MP}$.
* d) Sai. Vì $\overrightarrow{BP}-\overrightarrow{CP}=\overrightarrow{BP}+\overrightarrow{PC}=\overrightarrow{BC}$.

